1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:03,040
=Episode 4=

15
00:01:04,333 --> 00:01:07,200
Hello, I'm Jin Xi'en.
I'm coming back to work today.

16
00:01:09,888 --> 00:01:12,992
(WE Beauty Family)

17
00:01:13,266 --> 00:01:15,333
That's pretty much it for today.

18
00:01:15,333 --> 00:01:17,633
Okay.

19
00:01:24,533 --> 00:01:25,408
Miss Jin,

20
00:01:26,208 --> 00:01:27,360
last time...

21
00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:30,144
My neck is much better now.

22
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,966
What are you waiting for?
Help me get dressed.

23
00:01:44,266 --> 00:01:47,232
Are you disabled?
Can't you even dress yourself?

24
00:01:47,232 --> 00:01:48,400
Since you chose this job...

25
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:51,366
Alright, got it. I'll help you.

26
00:02:10,233 --> 00:02:11,766
Go prepare the car.

27
00:02:21,466 --> 00:02:22,966
(As we work together,)

28
00:02:23,066 --> 00:02:28,066
(I found he's dedicated, meticulous
and well-balanced in his work.)

29
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:31,900
(Except for being narcissistic,
childish, rude,)

30
00:02:32,133 --> 00:02:34,000
(opinionated, bad-tempered, etc.,)

31
00:02:34,266 --> 00:02:37,700
(I can tolerate him for now.)

32
00:02:38,233 --> 00:02:41,266
(In his office, there are many books
about fashion design)

33
00:02:41,566 --> 00:02:43,600
(and many of his costume drafts)

34
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:47,733
(which I think are infused
with emotion and passion.)

35
00:02:48,133 --> 00:02:50,066
(Unlike his work on beauty products,)

36
00:02:50,533 --> 00:02:52,333
(which is only cold data analysis.)

37
00:02:53,266 --> 00:02:55,100
(I also found his admission letter)

38
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:58,900
(Admission Letter)
(to Horton's best fashion university.)

39
00:02:59,966 --> 00:03:05,166
(However, his graduation photo shows
he went to a beauty design university.)

40
00:03:07,033 --> 00:03:10,966
(Anyway, I just need to hold on
until my sister returns.)

41
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:12,400
(I won't care so much.)

42
00:03:18,266 --> 00:03:22,366
I didn't expect the job to be so tiring.
It's like being a beast of burden.

43
00:03:22,933 --> 00:03:25,666
Xi'er, you've worked hard. Try this.

44
00:03:26,766 --> 00:03:28,133
This is my favorite.

45
00:03:35,466 --> 00:03:37,600
My appetite is gone. You eat them.

46
00:03:39,933 --> 00:03:43,466
What's wrong with you?
Don't waste my time again.

47
00:03:45,266 --> 00:03:48,733
Isn't this the macaron that Lan Chen
asked me to buy from downstairs?

48
00:03:49,366 --> 00:03:52,866
On my first day of work,
I found this downstairs of the company.

49
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:56,433
I really like to eat this, and...

50
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:04,100
I remember once after I worked overtime,
Mr. Lan drove me home.

51
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,520
Sorry, Miss Jin.

52
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:23,712
Actually, I chose you
because I didn't want my mom

53
00:04:24,333 --> 00:04:25,700
to put a snitch around me.

54
00:04:26,266 --> 00:04:27,933
But of course, you are excellent.

55
00:04:28,733 --> 00:04:32,100
If you feel it's not appropriate,
you can tell me.

56
00:04:32,566 --> 00:04:34,166
I'll get you another position.

57
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,500
The salary's the same.

58
00:04:44,933 --> 00:04:45,733
Miss Jin,

59
00:04:49,466 --> 00:04:52,866
this is a macaron from Mili,
sugar-free and calorie-free, easy on health.

60
00:04:53,766 --> 00:04:54,733
Thank you.

61
00:04:58,366 --> 00:04:59,333
Then I'm leaving.

62
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,533
When I got outside my house,

63
00:05:11,766 --> 00:05:13,566
he also gave me this.

64
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,000
We have very similar tastes.

65
00:05:18,933 --> 00:05:21,333
Now I know why you don't want to quit.

66
00:05:32,766 --> 00:05:33,566
Hello?

67
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:36,200
Miss Jin,
be at the office in five minutes.

68
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:37,366
Are you kidding me?

69
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:41,100
I'm off work now. Can't you let me rest?

70
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,066
Miss Jin, special circumstances.

71
00:05:43,166 --> 00:05:46,733
I'm off work.
Even a worker has the right to rest.

72
00:05:46,866 --> 00:05:50,166
I'm a secretary, not your nanny,
not at your beck and call.

73
00:05:53,166 --> 00:05:55,533
He hung up on me. What's wrong with him?

74
00:05:55,833 --> 00:05:58,966
He hung up on me. He can do whatever he wants
just because he's the CEO?

75
00:05:58,966 --> 00:05:59,600
Xi'er,

76
00:06:00,833 --> 00:06:06,700
there's no need to say it so...
After all, he is my boss.

77
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:20,700
Lan Chen?

78
00:06:23,633 --> 00:06:25,333
Mr. Lan, what are you doing here?

79
00:06:25,533 --> 00:06:26,333
That's right.

80
00:06:26,933 --> 00:06:28,966
As the CEO, I can do whatever I want.

81
00:06:29,633 --> 00:06:31,566
Since you don't want to
go to the company,

82
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,300
I had to come over.

83
00:06:38,366 --> 00:06:39,900
Are you insane? Get lost.

84
00:06:40,033 --> 00:06:40,833
Wait.

85
00:06:44,033 --> 00:06:46,720
Miss Jin, the banquet is about to start.

86
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:52,066
Mr. Zeng from Lihuai International
will attend too, so it's very important.

87
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:56,233
I don't want my secretary to be absent
from such an important occasion.

88
00:07:06,754 --> 00:07:11,276
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

89
00:07:14,306 --> 00:07:19,267
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

90
00:07:22,316 --> 00:07:28,140
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

91
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:34,656
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

92
00:07:35,610 --> 00:07:39,091
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

93
00:07:39,091 --> 00:07:43,212
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

94
00:07:43,212 --> 00:07:44,908
♪Open my secret♪

95
00:07:44,908 --> 00:07:50,956
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

96
00:07:50,956 --> 00:07:54,828
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

97
00:07:54,828 --> 00:07:59,334
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

98
00:08:01,376 --> 00:08:08,044
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
